# umockdev-run: 7 FILENAME_ARRAY repeatable flags
# + 1 NONE boolean + 1 STRING_ARRAY positional
# via empty-name sentinel, full OptionEntry[]
# static-table demonstration, Vala `[CCode (...)]`
# C-ABI attributes on bindings, `ref args` argv-
